ower, and rise as a Mythic Hero capable of deeds beyond mortal expectations.", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/pathfinder-wrath-of-the-righteous", "videos": [{"id": 33578, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "QoCBgO8qS70", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QoCBgO8qS70", "title": "Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous Kickstarter Campaign", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QoCBgO8qS70/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 53358, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "ttbj_9KH2PY", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ttbj_9KH2PY", "title": "Feature Trailer | Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ttbj_9KH2PY/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 53336, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "lj_G6QfStxE", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lj_G6QfStxE", "title": "Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous Feature trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lj_G6QfStxE/maxresdefault.jpg"}], "collections": [{"id": 2952, "name": "Pathfinder"}]}